gen relative\nto carbon agrees with other low-metallicity abundance measurements and suggests\nenrichment of the intergalactic medium by Type II supernovae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Jul 2002 23:35:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
